steall desc: Big Tony, the respected first-generation elder of the gangster apes, proudly introduced his successor - Stella. Her beauty and wisdom changed the structure within the gang and led them into a new era. Under Stella's leadership, the gang faces challenges, forges alliances, and navigates the complexities of jungle politics. As the story unfolds, Stella's character displays strength, emotion and commitment to the gangster tradition that captivates the jungle dwellers and leaves them eagerly anticipating the next chapter in the gangster gorilla saga.
